Title: Converter of SMILES in Canonical, Selfie, Inchi, Inchi Key form
Description: Using the Datamol package, the model receives a SMILE as input, then goes through a process of sanitizing and standardization of the molecule to generate four outputs: Canonical SMILES, SELFIES, InChI and InChIKey
Interpretation: Compound represented in its canonical SMILES, SELFIES, InChI and InChIKey forms
